# ${{ values.bucket_name }}

Secure S3 bucket definition generated by the platform S3 bucket template.

## Defaults

- public access is blocked
- server-side encryption is enabled with AES256
- object ownership is bucket-owner enforced
- versioning is configurable and enabled by default
- noncurrent object versions expire after `${{ values.lifecycle_expiration_days }}` days
- standard ownership, environment, and project tags are applied

## Usage

```bash
terraform init
terraform plan
terraform apply
```

Review `terraform.tfvars.example` and provide environment-specific values through your delivery workflow.
